Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: The inauguration of Gerald Ford as Vice President, 1973
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yqmjr
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 19 Oct 1973
A lack of procedure for the events following the resignation of Vice President Spiro Agnew, and the promotion of Gerald Ford from House Minority Leader to Vice President.